cs.CR, cs.SE, cs.PL, cs.SI, cs.DC

This paper focuses on analyzing web requests made by Android applications, which is closely related to security and privacy concerns (cs.CR). It also involves analyzing the code of Android applications to extract URLs, which falls under software engineering (cs.SE) and programming languages (cs.PL). The paper also discusses the performance of dynamic and static analyses, which could be relevant to systems and networking (cs.SI) and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC).
